651
00:58:10,010 --> 00:58:13,940
♫ Even if things don't go the way you want it ♫

652
00:58:13,940 --> 00:58:21,030
♫ Dream of the day that will someday shine ♫

653
00:58:21,030 --> 00:58:24,600
♫ At the end of a hard day ♫

654
00:58:24,600 --> 00:58:29,070
♫ put down the heavy burdens ♫

655
00:58:29,070 --> 00:58:36,560
♫ And try to breathe out the breath you've been holding ♫

656
00:58:36,560 --> 00:58:41,740
♫ It's okay even if it takes a little while ♫

657
00:58:41,740 --> 00:58:44,680
♫ Even if you run into ♫

658
00:58:44,680 --> 00:58:47,900
[Delivery Man]
♫ your difficult reality ♫

659
00:58:47,900 --> 00:58:50,710
Why are you coming out of here?

660
00:58:50,710 --> 00:58:54,140
You're in jail because of me.

661
00:58:54,140 --> 00:58:56,300
Let's look for Mr. Kim Jeong Wu first.

662
00:58:56,300 --> 00:58:59,100
This mansion belongs to nurse Kim Hui Yeon.

663
00:58:59,100 --> 00:59:00,740
She was here that day too.

664
00:59:00,740 --> 00:59:03,490
At the very least, we know that they didn't act alone.

665
00:59:03,490 --> 00:59:07,630
Kim Hui Yeon is suspicious, no matter how I look at it.

666
00:59:07,630 --> 00:59:10,030
Isn't this you?

667
00:59:10,030 --> 00:59:13,930
How did Detective Kang Ji Hyeon pass away?

668
00:59:13,930 --> 00:59:18,090
Do I have to catch the culprit, and relieve my grievances
to pass on?

669
00:59:18,090 --> 00:59:20,940
Do you want to disappear that much?

670
00:59:20,940 --> 00:59:23,480
I just saw something weird.

671
00:59:23,480 --> 00:59:28,210
♫ And try to breathe out the breath you've been holding ♫
